{"tid":2293253,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馮盈盈傳是舊TVB主席新寵 鄭衍峰代女友反擊：出個IG Post分分鐘買到兩、三個袋","createTime":"2020-11-20T06:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T07:39:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ac7f22c763b822b0a99b464edef8f077171d700a","tid":2293253,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:16:43.000Z","msg":"鄭衍峰開腔維護女友：「佢好慘，有少少戥佢唔抵。大家有冇諗過，藝人有好多side job，你出個活動、IG post，分分鐘已經買到兩、三個手袋。」他大讚盈盈是一個好勤力的藝人，還自爆為女友與網民理性討論：「佢EQ被訓練到睇得好化，反而今次佢同我講，我嬲過佢！」至於盈盈與江嘉敏已由好姊妹變死對頭，昨晚雖同場現身，但卻視而不見，大合照只各自各跟身旁的人傾偈，關係越鬧越僵。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201120/F32N5QIEO5EXROYYSI2MJDASXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201120%2FF32N5QIEO5EXROYYSI2MJDASXQ%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=085ee808\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201120%2FF32N5QIEO5EXROYYSI2MJDASXQ%2F&h=da5c02ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201120/F32N5QIEO5EXROYYSI2MJDASXQ/</a>"},{"pid":"8f5c4a5ec6bb02fa2d7df1c882842fe5516e03f3","tid":2293253,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:31:57.000Z","msg":"馮盈盈~ 逢見老闆笑盈盈~~"},{"pid":"94cea8a233e89c06d1c468d3fdbf8a948af203af","tid":2293253,"uid":158546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:34:02.000Z","msg":"唔係老細照邊有咁多Job<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通一樓一咁現金出糧咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c68b4ae3c4aad415bb9a775dea412345a195be","tid":2293253,"uid":228223,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"出個IG post就兩三隻，C朗夫人咪每個post千九幾隻？🇪🇦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm