kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:39:46.000Z","msg":"真係有新聞講過<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20190724/ZJFODZEWJALNXT7O4MAOHNVWCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20190724%2FZJFODZEWJALNXT7O4MAOHNVWCY%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=6d0db64c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20190724%2FZJFODZEWJALNXT7O4MAOHNVWCY%2F&h=455d2b48\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20190724/ZJFODZEWJALNXT7O4MAOHNVWCY/</a><br />\n<br />\n統計是根據各運動員IG上每一個贊助發文，該品牌的支出所得的數字，擁有運動員中最多追隨者的<span class=\"red\">C朗IG，平均每個發文高達78.4萬鎊（約760萬港元）</span>，遠超第二位尼馬的58萬鎊（約560萬港元）。前四位運動員都屬於足球範疇，尼馬之後分別是一post 52萬的美斯，以及28.7萬已退役的碧咸，到第5位才是籃球界的勒邦占士，一post為21.9萬。"}]}